Title: Fieldpiece vacuum pump 6cfm dualv
Description: Optimising the RunQuick oil management system, this Fieldpiece RunQuick oil change system, supplied complete with two cans of vacuum pump oil and a removeable oil sightglass, offers a clear view of the pump oil inside a system, allowing you to properly assess its quality. With this system oil can be replaced in less than 20 seconds, even while the pump is running, and with no loss of vacuum. A complete oil change is fast, clean and simple too. Lightweight and durable, the RunQuick oil change system's VP67UK vacuum pump is designed with a sturdy base to reduce the risk of spills as well as easy-use hose ports that ensure all hoses can be easily worked around.
